HEADWORD: Toledo
<hw>To*le"do</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sword or sword
blade made at <etsep>Toledo</etsep> in Spain, which city was famous in
the 16th and 17th centuries for the excellence of its weapons.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

